div.p: You sign up as a Cat Keeper or Cat-Sitter.
You fill out your profile with the basic info and a few feline facts about you. If you are a Cat Keeper, don't forget to add photo(s) of your cat(s).
As a Cat Keeper, you can post updates whenever you need a hand with your feline friend. You can choose who can see your update.
As a Cat-Sitter you can respond to visible updates in your area. If the Cat Keeper approves, they message you back and you can agree on the cat-handover.
